            <td>example time</td>
            <td>example total hours</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="policies">
        <div class="description">
          <p>
            Timesheet App, a project initiated by CoffeeCollab, aims to enhance
            our programming skills through the creation of a streamlined
            solution for managing timesheets. While not yet utilized by
            businesses, Timesheet App offers a comprehensive platform for
            tracking employee hours, facilitating efficient scheduling. By
            investing our efforts into this project, we strive to develop
            innovative tools that optimize productivity and elevate our
            programming expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
